    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Http_Client::request should allow additional options as second parameter in array form being set that will be passed to the currently set adapters write and read functions.</p>

<p>There might be adapters that allow/need per request options depending on the complexitly of the request/response ping pong, which currently can only be set by destroying and rebuilding the adapter.</p>

